From f09936cf31f88b4f7a3e17c4249741c129636f15 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Dario Pacule <dario@kuhula.finance>
Date: Tue, 23 Jun 2026 04:37:07 +0000
Subject: [PATCH 1/4] improve(ai): rewrite system prompt, session memory,
 optimised context and extended history

- Replace brittle CONTEXTO_FINANCEIRO_ATUAL wrapper with clean message history
- Rewrite system prompt in pt-MZ: clearer extraction rules, memory distinction,
  proactive data capture without unsolicited tool calls
- Add sessionMemoryRef to track mentioned-but-unregistered incomes/expenses
  across the full conversation; clears entries when a tool actually registers them
- Optimise context payload: compact state summary (total balance + last 8 txs)
  instead of full JSON with pretty-print, saving ~40% prompt tokens per call
- Extend history window from 14 to 30 messages (15 full turns) so long
  onboarding conversations like income/expense discovery don't lose context
- Remove redundant CONTEXTO_FINANCEIRO_ATUAL message-render filter (no longer needed)
